    "name": {
      "zh": "Tac-Kek JayPC 插板胸挂（橄榄绿）",
      "en": "Tac-Kek JayPC plate carrier (OD Green)"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "JayPC",
      "en": "JayPC"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "Crye Precision JPC 插板胸挂的廉价仿制品，水弹玩家下场专用。虽然穿着舒适性不如原版 JPC，但仍然具备基础的改装能力。有人把 IOTV 防弹衣上拆下来的肩垫装了上去，为下体提供额外防护。",
      "en": "A cheap airsoft bootleg of the Crye Precision JPC plate carrier. Doesn't offer the comfort of the original JPC, but retains extensive customization options. Someone attached an IOTV shoulder pad to this one to act as a groin protector."
    },
